# .env.local template for Movie Site
# Get your free TMDB API key from: https://www.themoviedb.org/settings/api
# Create new app, copy v3 auth "API Read Access Token" (starts with eyJ...)
# Then copy to .env.local file:

TMDB_API_KEY=74698a556085f62b7cf309bf7ea152fb

# IMPORTANT:
# 1. Copy this to .env.local (cp .env.example .env.local)
# 2. Replace 'your_tmdb_api_key_here' with your real key (keep quotes if spaces)
# 3. Restart dev server: npm run dev
# 4. Never commit .env.local (ignored by git)
